{"type": "article", "id": 9782, "title": "Hot Milk Lab “牛奶加工室”", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-20T07:12:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235432Mhd8BjHo5kwmaL0K.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">设计师 Sebastian Bergne 最近推出了一个“迷你实验室”，方便人们制作各种饮料。其中 Hot Milk Lab 专门方便人们在热牛奶里面加入各种配料，制作出不同风味的饮料。Sebastian Bergne 的这一套实验室由木制的托盘和不同型号的玻璃瓶，酒精灯以及托盘组成，烧牛奶的玻璃瓶中放置了一个温度计，可以方便使用者调节温度。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235428jncoArOfiYIS5mFe.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523542912F4Yr8JWCijagkz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235429LP1s82g3E5XoT946.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235430pRObIAHdW1Pu2g5k.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235430KsdZc9Teoa2VBtHJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354312iBqbjSJCL8YnURp.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235431Z6VknFP8G3K2NEBm.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<br>\n\n\n"}